reviewText: Though not up to other shows, specials, etc, that feature Richard Ayoude and Matt Berry, this does have some interest and fun.  Weakest part is the length- I was expecting something much much longer, and not thirty minutes.  Completists of the above artists would value this most.
arrived in perfect condition. There were no marks on the disk and everything was included, I purchased it used. It was more than I expected!
